---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About Me" description="Learn more about the author of this blog">
  <section>
    <h1 class="mb-6 text-3xl font-bold">About Me</h1>

    <div class="prose">
      <p>
        Hello! I'm a passionate web developer who loves to explore new technologies and share my
        findings through this blog.
      </p>

      <p>
        I created this blog using Astro, a modern static site generator that allows me to write
        content in Markdown while maintaining excellent performance.
      </p>

      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Framework:</strong> Astro</li>
        <li><strong>Styling:</strong> Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li><strong>Content:</strong> Markdown</li>
        <li><strong>Deployment:</strong> Vercel/Netlify</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why I Blog</h2>
      <p>
        Writing helps me clarify my thoughts and share knowledge with the wider developer community.
        I believe in learning in public and documenting my journey as I explore new technologies and
        techniques.
      </p>

      <h2>Connect With Me</h2>
      <p>Feel free to reach out through any of these channels:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://twitter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitter</a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="mailto:hello@example.com">Email</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
